I"•<p>In the <a href="../schedule.html">Schedule</a> you will notice days designated as individual project milestones.  These are opportunities for you to demonstrate progress on your individual project.</p>

<p>This document describes the expectations for each milestone.</p>

<p><em>Important</em>: For each milestone, make sure you come to class prepared to demonstrate your work.  If there is any hardware or software you need, it is your responsibility to make sure it is available and working.</p>

<p><em>Important</em>: Each individual milestone demo can be no longer than 2-4 minutes (in order for me to see all of the demos during class.)</p>

