<h2 id="expectations">Expectations</h2>

<p><strong>Milestone 1: Baseline Prototype</strong>.  You should be ready to demonstrate some concrete progress on your project in the form of a basic prototype.  The prototype should support some of the functionality described in your proposal, but it can be in a very basic form.</p>

<p><strong>Milestone 2: 50% Progress</strong>: For this milestone, you should be about half of the way towards completion of the project.  There should be some substantial progress towards completing the proposed work.</p>

<p><strong>Milestone 3: Final Project Demo</strong>. This is the completed project.</p>
